The 43-second video shows Malpas - who is wearing cream trousers, a red t-shirt and a brown jacket - jogging around the arena at the Canine Show at Stoneleigh Park, Warwickshire in front of an audience.

Incredibly, despite telling the DWP she was unable to walk very far and had poor mobility, the footage shows her jogging for three laps of the show ring.

Malpas, of Willenhall in the West Midlands, admitted falsely claiming the benefits when she was interviewed by investigators.

